    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with this absolute gem and honestly, it\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014it basically looks and feels brand new! It\u2019s been pampered in a garage, has zero scratches, and still has that wonderful fresh car smell. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I just know the next owner is going to be so happy. Come on by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
