    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2), featuring the naturally aspirated 3.8L MA1.01 flat-six engine with Direct Fuel Injection. This specimen is mechanically pristine, delivering 385 hp through a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. Equipped with the Sport Chrono Package and Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), the chassis provides exceptional torsional rigidity and razor-sharp turn-in. The vehicle boasts a flawless DME report with zero over-revs in ranges 2-6 and a documented service history confirming the integrity of the cooling system and AOS. Retaining its factory-spec finishes and original aerodynamic components, this is a rare opportunity to own the final iteration of the 911 featuring hydraulic steering rack feedback and pure analog engagement.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
