    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade 2012 Porsche 911 Carrera in a timeless Basalt Black Metallic finish. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showing no signs of road wear, stone chips, or paint imperfections. The exterior gleams with a deep, mirror-like luster thanks to a professional ceramic coating applied over factory-original paint. Inside, the Luxor Beige leather remains supple and taut, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma; the seat bolsters show no wear, and every piece of switchgear operates with a satisfying, factory-crisp click. Mechanically, this Carrera is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive, documented service history performed exclusively by authorized specialists. It drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor\u2014precise, powerful, and entirely vibration-free. Included in the sale are all original keys, the factory window sticker, and a detailed binder of every maintenance record since new. For the discerning buyer seeking a zero-excuses, showroom-quality icon, this example stands alone.",
